'
' ** Input Phase **
CLS                                         !***  Clear Screen   ***
INPUT "What is your name: ",surname$        !***       And       ***
INPUT "What is your age: ",age%             !*** Input Variables ***
'
' ** Process Phase **
MUL age%,12                                 !*** Convert Years To Months ***
'
' ** Output & End Phase **
PRINT CHR$(10);"Hello ";surname$;", you`re over ";age%;" months old!"
'
PRINT CHR$(7);                              !*** My Finish Routine, ***
VOID INP(2)                                 !***    Why Not Try     ***
EDIT                                        !***     Your Own?      ***
